e":"Adam","meanings":["Hebrew: The Scripture name, in Hebrew, Adham, signifying 'man;' literally earthy, red earth; Rudolph, however, says the name in Ethiopic means ' to be fair, beautiful.' Hence the nurse-name Addy, little Adam."]},{"name":"Addams","meanings":["English: variant of   Adams  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Adams was born about 1365, in Wales. She had at least 1 son with Nicholas Adams."},"et":{"about 1365–":"umbes 1365–Surnud","1362–Male":"1362–Surnud","1393–Male":"1393–Surnud","1365–Female":"1365–Surnud","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","about 1365":"umbes 1365","1393":"1393","Buckspool, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales"},"fi":{"about 1365–":"noin 1365–Kuollut","1362–Male":"1362–Kuollut","1393–Male":"1393–Kuollut","1365–Female":"1365–Kuollut","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","about 1365":"noin 1365","1393":"1393","Buckspool, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales"},"fr":{"about 1365–":"environ 1365–Décédée","1362–Male":"1362–Décédé","1393–Male":"1393–Décédé","1365–Female":"1365–Décédée","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","about 1365":"environ 1365","1393":"1393","Buckspool, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Galles","Wales":"Galles","lifeSummary":"Adams est née environ 1365, à Galles. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Nicholas Adams."},"de":{"about 1365–":"um 1365–Verstorben","1362–Male":"1362–Verstorben","1393–Male":"1393–Verstorben","1365–Female":"1365–Verstorben","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","about 1365":"um 1365","1393":"1393","Buckspool, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales","lifeSummary":"Adams wurde um 1365 in Wales geboren. Sie hatte mit Nicholas Adams mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1365–":"about 1365–Desede","1362–Male":"1362–Desede","1393–Male":"1393–Desede","1365–Female":"1365–Desede","1365":"1365","1362":"1362","about 1365":"about 1365","1393":"1393","Buckspool, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Wales":"Wales"},"hu":{"about 1365–":"1365 körül–elhunyt","1362–Male":"1362–elhunyt"